CHANGES IN VERSION 1.13
-----------------------

BUG FIXES

    o Added 'ZipData: no' to the template, which
    caused problems on Windows systems.

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.11
-----------------------

USER VISIBLE CHANGES

    o For Gene and Exon arrays, all PM probes are in
    the pmfeature table (matching what happens with
    expression arrays)

    o Updated package template to require oligo (>= 1.11.18)

BUG FIXES

    o Fixed creation of indices for Gene arrays
